name: Early Stage HER2+ (Draft)
description: Pathway for the Early Stage HER2+ Initial Medical Consult Breast Cancer Pathway. This is a draft pathway.

preconditions.cql: exists("Primary Cancer Condition" PrimaryCancer where PrimaryCancer.code.text.value ~ 'Malignant neoplasm of breast (disorder)')
exists([Observation: "HER2 [Presence] in Breast cancer specimen by Immune stain"] Her2 where Her2.value.text.value ~ 'Positive')

condition.cql: exists([Observation: "Regional lymph nodes.clinical [Class] Cancer code"] N0 where ToConcept(N0.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "N0 category (finding)")

exists([Observation: "Regional lymph nodes.clinical [Class] Cancer code"] NLarge where ToConcept(NLarge.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "N1 category (finding)" or ToConcept(NLarge.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "N2 category (finding)" or ToConcept(NLarge.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "N3 category (finding)")

exists([Observation: "Primary tumor.clinical [Class] Cancer code"] TLarge where ToConcept(TLarge.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "T2 category (finding)" or ToConcept(TLarge.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "T3 category (finding)")

exists([Observation: "Primary tumor.clinical [Class] Cancer code"] TSmall where ToConcept(TSmall.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "T0 category (finding)" or ToConcept(TSmall.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "T1 category (finding)")

action.description: Post Chemotherapy Trastuzumab (1 year total duration recommended)

condition.cql: exists([Observation: "Estrogen receptor Ag [Presence] in Breast cancer specimen by Immune stain code"] Pos where ToConcept(Pos.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept) ~ "Positive (qualifier value)")
